<HEADLINE>  Clinton Seeks Hurricane Mitch Aid </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	WASHINGTON (AP) -- President Clinton will ask Congress to provide  
enhanced trade benefits to countries of Central America and the 
Caribbean to help them recover from the devastation of Hurricane 
Mitch. 
</P>
