<HEADLINE> Minnelli To Sing at MAC Awards </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- Life is still a cabaret for Liza Minnelli.  
</P>
<P>
	Minnelli, who starred in the 1972 film ``Cabaret'' and often  
attends the music clubs in New York, will sing for the first time 
at the upcoming MAC awards, which honor cabaret entertainers. 
</P>
<P>
